unty Hunters|The Bounty Hunters]]'')\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 4#The Sith in Shadow|The Sith in Shadow]]'' by [[Bob Harris (writer)|Bob Harris]] (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 4#Star Wars Tales 13|''Tales''#13]])\n\n''25 BBY''\n* ''[[Poison Moon]]'' by [[Michael Carriglitto]] (published in Dark Horse Extra #44\u201347)\n\n''24 BBY''\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 3#A Jedi's Weapon|A Jedi's Weapon]]'' by Henry Gilroy (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 3#Star Wars Tales 12|''Tales''#12]])\n* ''[[Starfighter: Crossbones]]'' by Haden Blackman\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 4#Puzzle Peace|Puzzle Peace]]'' by [[Scott Beatty]] (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 4#Star Wars Tales 13|''Tales''#13]])\n* ''[[Star Wars Republic: Honor and Duty|Honor and Duty]]'' by [[John Ostrander]] (''[[Star Wars: Republic]]'' #46\u201348)\n\n''23 BBY''\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 5#Way of the Warrior|Way of the Warrior]]'' by Peter Alilunas (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 5#Star Wars Tales 18|''Tales''#18]])\n* ''Full of Surprises'' by [[Jason Hall (writer)|Jason Hall]] (published in [[Hasbro]]/[[Toys\"R\"Us]] Exclusive)\n* ''Most Precious Weapon'' by [[Jason Hall (writer)|Jason Hall]] (published in Hasbro/Toys\"R\"Us Exclusive)\n* ''Practice Makes Perfect'' by [[Jason Hall (writer)|Jason Hall]] (published in Hasbro/Toys\"R\"Us Exclusive)\n* ''Machines of War'' by [[Jason Hall (writer)|Jason Hall]] (published in Hasbro/Toys\"R\"Us Exclusive)\n\n====Attack of the Clones/The Clone Wars====\n''22 BBY''\n\n* ''[[Clone Wars (comic book)|Clone Wars]] Volume 1: The Defense of Kamino'' by John Ostrander, Jan Duursema, Haden Blackman and Scott Allie (Published by Titan Books Ltd.)\n** ''[[Star Wars Republic 49: Sacrifice|Sacrifice]]'' by [[John Ostrander]] (''[[Star Wars: Republic|Republic]]'' #49)\n** ''[[Star Wars Republic 50: The Battle of Kamino|The Battle of Kamino]]'' by [[John Ostrander]], Haden Blackman and [[Scott Allie]] (''[[Star Wars: Republic|Republic]]'' #50)\