ift From Alderaan '' by [[Chris Claremont]]\n* ''Classic Star Wars: A Long Time Ago... Volume 4: Screams in the Void'' (collects Marvel's ''[[Star Wars (1977 comic book)|Star Wars]]'' #54\u201367 & Annual #2)\n* ''Classic Star Wars: A Long Time Ago... Volume 5: Fool's Bounty'' (collects Marvel's ''[[Star Wars (1977 comic book)|Star Wars]]'' #68\u201381 & Annual #3)\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 1#Moment of Doubt|Moment of Doubt]]'' by [[Lovern Kindzierski]] (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 1#Star Wars Tales 4|''Tales''#4]])\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 4#Slippery Slope|Slippery Slope]]'' by [[Scott Lobdell]] (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 4#Star Wars Tales 15|''Tales''#15]])\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 2#Thank the Maker|Thank the Maker]]'' by [[Ryder Windham]] (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 2#Star Wars Tales 6|''Tales''#6]])\n* ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 5#Hunger Pains|Hunger Pains]]'' by [[Jim Campbell (comics)|Jim Campbell]] (published in [[Star Wars Tales Volume 5#Star Wars Tales 20|''Tales''#20]])\n* ''Blind Fury'' by [[Alan Moore]] (published in ''Devilworlds'' #1)\n* ''Tales from Mos Eisley'' by [[Bruce Jones (comics)|Bruce Jones]]\n* ''[[Shadow Stalker]]'' by Ryder Windham\n* ''[[Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire (comic)|Shadows of the Empire]]'' by [[John Wagner]]\n* ''[[Battle of the Bounty Hunters]]'' pop-up comic by [[Ryder Windham]]\n* ''[[Star Wars: The Bounty Hunters#The Bounty Hunters: Scoundrel's Wages|Scoundrel's Wages]]'' by [[Mark Schultz (comics)|Mark Schultz]] (published in ''[[Star Wars: The Bounty Hunters|The Bounty Hunters]]'')\n* ''[[Star Wars Adventures]]: [[Luke Skywalker]] and the Treasure of the Dragonsnakes'' by [[Tom Taylor (writer)|Tom Taylor]]\n* ''[[Star Wars Adventures]]: The Will of Darth Vader'' by [[Tom Taylor (writer)|Tom Taylor]]\n\n====''Return of the Jedi''====\n''4 ABY''\n* ''Mara Jade: By the Emperor's Hand'' by [[Timothy Zahn]] and [[Michael A. Stackpole]]\n* ''The Jabba Tape'' by [[John Wagner]]\n